text: The Heung Yee Kuk, is a functional constituency in the elections for the Legislative Council of Hong Kong first created in 1991. The constituency is composed of the Chairman and Vice-Chairmen of the Heung Yee Kuk and the Ex Officio, Special and Co-opted Councillors of the Full Council of the Kuk. ==References== Category:Functional constituencies of Hong Kong
title: Heung Yee Kuk (constituency)
